#160;</span>\n<h2 style="font-size:100%;font-weight:bold;border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em;"><span class="mw-headline" id="WikiProjects"><i>WikiProjects</i></span></h2>\n</div>\n<div style="display: block; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; vertical-align: top; background: #f9f9ff; color: black; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 1em; margin-top: 0em; padding-top: .3em;">\n<ul>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Railways_in_India" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Railways in India">WikiProject Railways in India</a> (<a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:INRI" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:INRI">WP:INRI</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Similar WikiProjects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Stations" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Stations">WikiProject Stations</a> (<a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:STA" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:STA">WP:STA</a>)</li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Rapid_transit" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Rapid transit">WikiProject Rapid transit</a> (<a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:RTPJ" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:RTPJ">WP:RTPJ</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>by region:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Metros_of_the_former_Soviet_Union" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Metros of the former Soviet Union">WikiProject Metros of the former Soviet Union</a> (<a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:SOVMETRO" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:SOVMETRO">WP:SOVMETRO</a>)</li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Rail_transport_in_Jamaica" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Rail transport in Jamaica">WikiProject Rail transport in Jamaica</a></li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Trains_in_Japan" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Trains in Japan">WikiProject Trains in Japan</a> (<a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:TJ" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:TJ">WP:TJ</a>)</li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_NZR" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject NZR">WikiProject New Zealand Railways</a> (<a href="/wiki/Wik